channel.title: 34K Massive Model Pack
channel.description:
[QUOTE]Well over the year and a half I've been lurking around this site, I've managed to compile a huge pack of models that I've downloaded.
The pack contains many actual JaGeX items, and custom made items.
I take no credits for the making of any of these models, with the exception of the Dual Greataxes, and Bladeshield.
This model pack even includes other peoples model packs :P
The pack includes models for all the items listed, ints for most of them, and 90% of them are already gzipped
Programs included:
Metasequoia Gzip Kevin and InzInz's Color Picker RSMV Datmaker v1.3
Here are some pictures of what you're getting.
Properties: [IMG]http://img690.imageshack.us/img690/2379/propertypage.png[/img]
List of all the files: [IMG]http://img27.imageshack.us/img27/5280/propertieso.png[/img]
Cheers and happy modeling :]
Link: [URL=http://www.mediafire.com/?nidjutk4qye]http://www.mediafire.com/?nidjutk4qye[/URL]
[/QUOTE]
A massive pack of models I found on another RSPS community site.
Credits: .00001% Me for spreading the massive pack. (I don't want rep for something I put 2 seconds of work into...)
25% to the poster, for the collecting and packaging of all these models.
Rest to the creators of the custom models and JaGeX ofc.
Enjoy.
